  <!-- ── Limitations ────────────────────────── -->
  <h2 class="section-heading" id="limitations" data-jump-label="Current Cowork Limitations">What Cowork Can't Do (Yet)</h2>
  <p class="section-description">To set proper expectations:</p>

  <ul class="limitation-list">
    <li><strong>Can't access cloud storage directly</strong> — Files need to be on your local machine or synced locally</li>
    <li><strong>Can't interact with web applications</strong> — That's Claude Code territory</li>
    <li><strong>Can't run indefinitely</strong> — Very long operations may need to be broken into chunks</li>
    <li><strong>Can't access files you don't have permissions for</strong> — System files, other user folders, etc.</li>
  </ul>

