  <!-- ── Takeaways ────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="takeaways">
    <h3>Key Takeaways</h3>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Cowork = Claude that can act</strong>, not just talk</li>
      <li><strong>Use it for file operations</strong>, data analysis, and multi-step workflows</li>
